	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I love Chrono Trigger. Today I got out my SNES and the CT cart only to turn it on and find my saves were gone and the menu's ( main and ingame) are garbled and glitch and impossible to navigate. I've tried cleaning the contacts but that wouldn't work. My SNES runs other games just fine (SMW, SMRPG, A Link the Past, etc). Any ideas on what this could be?<br /><div class="attachtitle">Attachment:</div><div class="attachcontent">
			<a href="./download/file.php?id=1898&amp;mode=view"><img src="./download/file.php?id=1898&amp;t=1" alt="image.jpg" /></a><br />
			<span class="gensmall">image.jpg [ 1.72 MiB | Viewed 346 times ]</span>
		

		<br />
	</div><br />( this is the main menu, the in game one looks similar).

		

		</td>
