	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Pin 54 on the edge connector also looks damaged, and that's the cart /WR signal, which could easily cause this kind of corruption if the game is using the cart SRAM as work RAM, not just save storage.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


